## 🔬 Mathematical Foundation

The framework implements quantum-inspired operations:

### Entanglement Correlation

```bash
|ψ⟩ = α|00⟩ + β|11⟩
Correlation(i,j) = ⟨ψᵢ|ψⱼ⟩ · exp(-γ·d(i,j))
```

### Quantum State Evolution

```bash
|ψ(t+1)⟩ = U(θ)|ψ(t)⟩
U(θ) = exp(-iH·θ)
```

### Decoherence Modeling

```bash
ρ(t) = (1-λ)ρ(t-1) + λ·I/d
```

